txt.en: This axe was carried by a Dunlending, but you see markings that are clearly not of Dunlending-make. While you cannot tell the origin of the craftsmanship, perhaps one of the Elves in Gwingris will know more.

'This is strange. You say this was carried by one of the Dunlendings nearby?\n\n'This axe is of a quality not normally known to these brigands and bodes ill. It seems that what would normally be an independent force has organized under someone else's banner.'
You have found a strange axe on one of the Dunlendings near Gwingris, but you do not recognize the craftsmanship.
Bring the axe to Inufileg in Gwingris
